data.description: Welcome to a spacious 5 bedroom 3 full bathroom home featuring an open concept layout, ideal for modern living. Enjoy the expansive backyard, perfect for outdoor activities, along with a covered patio for all-weather relaxation. This home features installed outdoor lighting that can be adjusted for all seasonal holidays! Minor cosmetic touch-ups needed, but overall, an excellent opportunity to own a great, well-designed home!!
